summary: I combine my passion for teaching, philosophy and movement in my career. As a teacher of Greek and Latin in high school, I hope to inspire students to think critically and develop their own world view. It is my mission to make good education more accessible for kids of all backgrounds. Moreover, the balance between mind and body is crucial for effective learning. In modern society, the pressure to perform is high. Yoga and mindfulness teach us to be more compassionate to ourselves and others. I believe in learning from a place of calmness, confidence and curiosity! As a certified yoga teacher I help people to reconnect to their body and to find more freedom through movement.
